### =========================
### PERMISSIONS
### =========================

### Create Permission
POST http://localhost:3001/permissions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "user:create",
    "method": "POST",
    "path": "/users"
}

###

### Create another Permission (for later role assignment tests)
POST http://localhost:3001/permissions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "user:read",
    "method": "GET",
    "path": "/users"
}

###

### Get all Permissions
GET http://localhost:3001/permissions HTTP/1.1

###

### Get one Permission by id
GET http://localhost:3001/permissions/8cf899b5-ef55-4551-ac81-a142669c8130 HTTP/1.1

###

### Update Permission
PATCH http://localhost:3001/permissions/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "user:create",
    "method": "POST",
    "path": "/users"
}

###

### Delete Permission
DELETE http://localhost:3001/permissions/485ae64b-eb20-4dee-bc5e-033e556781c9 HTTP/1.1

###


### =========================
### ROLES
### =========================

### Create Role
POST http://localhost:3001/roles HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "administrator"
}

###

### Create Role with permissionIds directly
POST http://localhost:3001/roles HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "author",
    "permissionIds": ["8cf899b5-ef55-4551-ac81-a142669c8130"]
}

###

### Get all Roles
GET http://localhost:3001/roles HTTP/1.1

###

### Get one Role by id
GET http://localhost:3001/roles/63604bfa-196b-4880-b9e9-47411f1442d7 HTTP/1.1

###

### Update Role (name and/or permissionIds)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/roles/63604bfa-196b-4880-b9e9-47411f1442d7 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "moderator",
    "permissionIds": ["8cf899b5-ef55-4551-ac81-a142669c8130"]
}

###

### Assign Permissions to Role by name (used by seed script)
POST http://localhost:3001/roles/administrator/permissions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "permissions": ["user:create", "user:read"]
}

###

### Delete Role
DELETE http://localhost:3001/roles/485ae64b-eb20-4dee-bc5e-033e556781c9 HTTP/1.1

###



















